<lb n="0188a13" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0188a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0188a15" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 861</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0188a16" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0188002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】延享元年刊大正大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫本高山寺藏豐山版</note>毘盧遮那五字真言修習儀軌</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0188a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0188a18" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">三藏<note n="0188003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不空金剛＝金剛不空智奉【甲】</note><note n="0188003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不空金剛【大】，金剛不空智奉【甲】</note><app n="0188003"><lem wit="【大】">不空金剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">金剛不空智奉</rdg></app>　<note n="0188004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（奉）ヵ＋詔【原】</note><note n="0188004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詔【大】，奉詔【考偽-原】</note><app n="0188004"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">詔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">奉詔</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0188a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188a1901">夫修習成就毘盧遮那佛法，先應於閑淨處
<lb n="0188a20" ed="T"/>以瞿摩夷塗地，香水散灑，燒種種名香，散種
<lb n="0188a21" ed="T"/>種時花，當於寂靜<note n="0188005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝辭ヵ【原】</note><note n="0188005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦【大】，辭【考偽-原】</note><app n="0188005"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">辦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">辭</rdg></app>喧鬧，清淨澡浴著新
<lb n="0188a22" ed="T"/>淨衣結跏趺坐。或<note n="0188006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">依＋（求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏）【甲】</note><note n="0188006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">依【大】，依求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏【甲】</note><app n="0188006"><lem wit="【大】">依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">依求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏</rdg></app>類而坐：息災吉祥<note n="0188007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【甲】＊</note><note n="0188007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐【大】＊，座【甲】＊</note><app n="0188007"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188a23" ed="T"/>面向北；增益蓮花<app type="star" corresp="#0188007"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>面向東；敬愛金剛<app type="star" corresp="#0188007"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188a24" ed="T"/>面向西；降伏蹲踞<app type="star" corresp="#0188007"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>以脚押脚面向南。</p><p xml:id="pT18p0188a2416" rend="inline">隨所
<lb n="0188a25" ed="T"/>愛樂依方而坐，即以香泥塗手，於頂上合掌
<lb n="0188a26" ed="T"/>禮敬一切諸佛。然於下方從風輪起想「<note n="0188008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩＝縛【甲】＊</note><note n="0188008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】＊，縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>」字，
<lb n="0188a27" ed="T"/>以二點嚴飾，如<note n="0188009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">金＋（剛）【甲】</note><note n="0188009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金【大】，金剛【甲】</note><app n="0188009"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">金剛</rdg></app>形放熾盛光，威猛赫<note n="0188a2701" resp="CBETA" type="add">奕【CB】，弈【大】</note><app n="0188a2701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">奕</lem><rdg wit="【大】">弈</rdg></app>；金
<lb n="0188a28" ed="T"/>剛火焰壞破大地，上衝流出，則想此金剛火
<lb n="0188a29" ed="T"/>焰焚燒自身，乃至灰<note n="0188010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謝＝<g ref="#CB13789"/>【甲】</note><note n="0188010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謝【大】，<g ref="#CB13789"/>【甲】</note><app n="0188010"><lem wit="【大】">謝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><g ref="#CB13789"/></rdg></app>隨四種法色；想灰成
<pb n="0188b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0861.0188b"/>
<lb n="0188b01" ed="T"/>曼拏羅，即於曼荼羅中想一蓮花；於蓮花中
<lb n="0188b02" ed="T"/>想「<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>」字轉成金剛形；想己身為金剛所成。</p>
<lb n="0188b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b0301">即結三昧耶印：二手作三普吒掌，竪二大
<lb n="0188b04" ed="T"/>指加持於五處。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b0501" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱喃　阿三迷　怛哩<note n="0188011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><note n="0188011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0188011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三迷　三
<lb n="0188b06" ed="T"/>摩曳　莎縛<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note n="0188012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0188012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0188b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b0701">次結法界印：二手作拳，二大指在掌中竪
<lb n="0188b08" ed="T"/>二頭指；想<note n="0188013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【甲】</note><note n="0188013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，羅【甲】</note><app n="0188013"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app>字於頂上，思惟真實義，一切
<lb n="0188b09" ed="T"/>法塵不可得。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b1001" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱喃　達<note n="0188014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝磨【甲】</note><note n="0188014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩【大】，磨【甲】</note><app n="0188014"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">磨</rdg></app>馱<note n="0188015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＝覩【甲】</note><note n="0188015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">都【大】，覩【甲】</note><app n="0188015"><lem wit="【大】">都</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">覩</rdg></app>　娑嚩婆嚩
<lb n="0188b11" ed="T"/>俱<note n="0188016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吽＝唅【甲】</note><note n="0188016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𤙖【大】，唅【甲】</note><app n="0188016"><lem wit="【大】">𤙖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唅</rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0188b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b1201">次結次輪印：二手反相叉，<note n="0188017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝左【甲】</note><note n="0188017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，左【甲】</note><app n="0188017"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">左</rdg></app>大指在右手
<lb n="0188b13" ed="T"/>掌中相著；觀自身為金剛薩埵，合以加持。真
<lb n="0188b14" ed="T"/>言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b1501" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多　<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0188b03"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　喃　<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0188b05"/>囉<note place="inline">二合、<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0188b06"/>引</note>
<lb n="0188b16" ed="T"/>　怛摩　俱唅」</p>
<lb n="0188b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b1701">次結甲冑印：二手三普吒掌，二頭指屈<note n="0188018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】</note><note n="0188018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄【大】，跓【甲】</note><app n="0188018"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188b18" ed="T"/>中指背上節，二大指並竪合在掌印五處。真
<lb n="0188b19" ed="T"/>言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b2001" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　喃　<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅迦　<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>遮
<lb n="0188b21" ed="T"/>　吽」</p>
<lb n="0188b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b2201">則於自身前想大蓮華王，於蓮華中想金色
<lb n="0188b23" ed="T"/>「佉」字，其「佉」字轉成婆伽梵大勤勇尊，住之三
<lb n="0188b24" ed="T"/>摩地，結劍印。即結如來鉤印奉請本尊：<note n="0188019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＋（手）【甲】</note><note n="0188019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，二手【甲】</note><app n="0188019"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二手</rdg></app>內
<lb n="0188b25" ed="T"/>相叉作拳，竪右頭指如鉤向身招之。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b2601" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱喃　<note n="0188020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噁＝惡【甲】</note><note n="0188020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">噁【大】，惡【甲】</note><app n="0188020"><lem wit="【大】">噁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惡</rdg></app>娑<note n="0188021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔囉〕－【甲】</note><note n="0188021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0188021"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩怛<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0188b09"/>囉　鉢羅
<lb n="0188b27" ed="T"/>底訶多　怛多<note n="0188022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘖＋（多）【甲】，（黨）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0188022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘖【大】，蘖多【甲】，蘖黨【考偽-原】</note><app n="0188022"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">蘖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘖多</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">蘖黨</rdg></app>俱舍　<g ref="#CB00155"/>地者哩耶　鉢哩布<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0188b10"/>囉
<lb n="0188b28" ed="T"/>迦　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0188b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188b2901">聖眾來已，即奉閼伽，二手<note n="0188023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捧＋（器）【甲】</note><note n="0188023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捧【大】，捧器【甲】</note><app n="0188023"><lem wit="【大】">捧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捧器</rdg></app>當額想浴聖
<pb n="0188c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0861.0188c"/>
<lb n="0188c01" ed="T"/>眾。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c0201" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱喃　哦哦那　三摩三摩　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188c03" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0188c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c0401">次獻敷座印：二手虛心合掌，散舒<note n="0188024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屈＋（頭中名）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0188024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屈【大】，屈頭中名【考偽-原】</note><app n="0188024"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">屈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">屈頭中名</rdg></app>六指
<lb n="0188c05" ed="T"/>如蓮花形。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c0601" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱<note n="0188025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃＝南【甲】＊</note><note n="0188025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喃【大】＊，南【甲】＊</note><app n="0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>　噁」</p>
<lb n="0188c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c0701">次結聖不動尊印：二手各作拳，各竪頭中
<lb n="0188c08" ed="T"/>指，各以二大指押無名指、小指，左手為鞘，右
<lb n="0188c09" ed="T"/>手為刀，以刀左旋轉辟除諸魔障，右旋轉及
<lb n="0188c10" ed="T"/>上下成方隅界。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c1101" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多　<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>　𧹞戰拏　摩訶嚧灑拏
<lb n="0188c12" ed="T"/>　薩叵吒耶　吽　怛<note n="0188026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＋（二合）ヵ夾註【原】</note><note n="0188026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，囉(二合)【考偽-原】</note><app n="0188026"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">囉(二合)</rdg></app>吒　<note n="0188027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𤙖＝吽【甲】</note><note n="0188027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𤙖【大】，吽【甲】</note><app n="0188027"><lem wit="【大】">𤙖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">吽</rdg></app>　𤚥」</p>
<lb n="0188c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c1301">復以刀印觸香花<note n="0188028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">求＝水【甲】，等ヵ【原】</note><note n="0188028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求【大】，水【甲】，等【考偽-原】</note><app n="0188028"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">等</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">水</rdg></app>無垢令淨，以成加護置
<lb n="0188c14" ed="T"/>於鞘中。</p>
<lb n="0188c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c1501">次結毘盧遮那五字劍印：二手合掌屈二頭，
<lb n="0188c16" ed="T"/>指相著如劍形。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c1701" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱喃　阿尾<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0188c04"/>囉　吽　欠」</p>
<lb n="0188c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c1801">次結塗香印：右手掌向外，以左手<note n="0188029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">握＝掘【甲】</note><note n="0188029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">握【大】，掘【甲】</note><app n="0188029"><lem wit="【大】">握</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">掘</rdg></app>右手
<lb n="0188c19" ed="T"/>腕如環。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c2001" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱<app type="star" corresp="#0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>　尾<g ref="#CB02122"/>駄<note n="0188030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巘＝獻【甲】</note><note n="0188030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巘【大】，獻【甲】</note><app n="0188030"><lem wit="【大】">巘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">獻</rdg></app>塗納婆吠　娑
<lb n="0188c21" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0188c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c2201">次結花印：二手內相叉，仰掌頭指<note n="0188031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（相）＋著【甲】</note><note n="0188031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">著【大】，相著【甲】</note><app n="0188031"><lem wit="【大】">著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">相著</rdg></app>，二大
<lb n="0188c23" ed="T"/>指安頭指下節。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c2401" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱<app type="star" corresp="#0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>　摩訶每怛哩耶<note place="inline">二合</note>　毘愈
<lb n="0188c25" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>娜蘖底　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0188c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c2601">次結燒香印：二手中指、無名指、小指背合
<lb n="0188c27" ed="T"/>竪，頭指直竪傾相合，大指在頭指下節。真言
<lb n="0188c28" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0188c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0188c2901" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱<app type="star" corresp="#0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>　達摩駄<note n="0188032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覩嚩娜＝暏拏【甲】</note><note n="0188032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">覩嚩娜【大】，暏拏【甲】</note><app n="0188032"><lem wit="【大】">覩嚩娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">暏拏</rdg></app>蘖帝
<pb n="0189a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0861.0189a"/>
<lb n="0189a01" ed="T"/>　<note n="0189001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝婆【甲】</note><note n="0189001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎【大】，婆【甲】</note><app n="0189001"><lem wit="【大】">莎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0189a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a0201">次結飲食<note n="0189002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言〕－【甲】</note><note n="0189002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真言【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0189002"><lem wit="【大】">真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>印：當合定惠掌，五輪互相
<lb n="0189a03" ed="T"/>叉，是則持眾物，普通供養印。</p>
<lb n="0189a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a0401" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱喃　阿<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189a03"/>囉<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189a04"/>囉迦<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189a05"/>囉<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189a06"/>囉<note n="0189003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末＝未【甲】＊</note><note n="0189003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">末【大】＊，未【甲】＊</note><app n="0189003"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a05" ed="T"/>　隣捺那<note n="0189004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迷＋（摩隣上聲娜泥摩訶麼理）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0189004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迷【大】，迷摩隣上聲娜泥摩訶麼理【考偽-原】</note><app n="0189004"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">迷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">迷摩隣上聲娜泥摩訶麼理</rdg></app>　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0189a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a0601">次結<note n="0189005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">燈＋（明）【甲】</note><note n="0189005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燈【大】，燈明【甲】</note><app n="0189005"><lem wit="【大】">燈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">燈明</rdg></app>印：右手作拳，中指直竪，頭指屈<note n="0189006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大捻＝捻大【甲】</note><note n="0189006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大捻【大】，捻大【甲】</note><app n="0189006"><lem wit="【大】">大
<lb n="0189a07" ed="T"/>捻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捻大</rdg></app>，指博附中指。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0189a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a0801" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱<app type="star" corresp="#0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>　多他蘖多　哩紙　薩叵<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189a10"/>囉
<lb n="0189a09" ed="T"/>拏<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>婆娑那　哦哦那　烏馱哩耶　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶
<lb n="0189a10" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0189a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a1101">所獻塗香、花鬘、燒香、飲食、燈明，隨四種法色
<lb n="0189a12" ed="T"/>而以供養，由五種供養印，成於聖眾集會普
<lb n="0189a13" ed="T"/>遍香花等雲海供養。</p>
<lb n="0189a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a1401">次結圓滿印：二手虛心合掌安於頂上。真
<lb n="0189a15" ed="T"/>言曰：</p>
<lb n="0189a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a1601" cb:type="dharani">「那謨　三曼多沒馱<app type="star" corresp="#0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>　噁尾　娑摩曳　娑叵<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189a15"/>囉　呬
<lb n="0189a17" ed="T"/>𤚥　哦哦那　劍達　摩馱怛<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>迦舍　三摩多耶　娑
<lb n="0189a18" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>　怛他<note n="0189007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘖＋（多）【甲】</note><note n="0189007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘖【大】，蘖多【甲】</note><app n="0189007"><lem wit="【大】">蘖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘖多</rdg></app>　<note n="0189008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跛＝跋ヵ【原】</note><note n="0189008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跛【大】，跋【考偽-原】</note><app n="0189008"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">跋</rdg></app>哩<note n="0189009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剎＝殺【甲】</note><note n="0189009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">剎【大】，殺【甲】</note><app n="0189009"><lem wit="【大】">剎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">殺</rdg></app>　曼荼羅　摩摩本惹<app type="star" corresp="#0189003"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a19" ed="T"/>禮拏　怛他蘖多　地瑟姹　那<app type="star" corresp="#0189003"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>禮那遮迷　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a20" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0189a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a2101">由此真言印、香花等雲海供養，如實<note n="0189010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（異）【甲】</note><note n="0189010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，無異【甲】</note><app n="0189010"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">無異</rdg></app>，即用
<lb n="0189a22" ed="T"/>五字從下體布至頂，地、水、火、風、空，即想自身
<lb n="0189a23" ed="T"/>如金色毘盧遮那佛，<note n="0189011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＋（身）ヵ【原】，（放）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0189011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍【大】，遍身【考偽-原】，遍放【考偽-原】</note><app n="0189011"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">遍身</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">遍放</rdg></app>光明頭冠瓔珞身著
<lb n="0189a24" ed="T"/>紗縠衣。即結劍印：安於當心住三摩地，二手
<lb n="0189a25" ed="T"/>持珠，合於掌中誦真言七遍，加持安<note n="0189012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【甲】</note><note n="0189012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0189012"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頂
<lb n="0189a26" ed="T"/>上。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0189a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a2701" cb:type="dharani">「唵　吠盧者那　摩羅　娑<app type="star" corresp="#0188008"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0189a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189a2801">然後二手當心，持珠念誦本尊<note n="0189013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（真）＋言【甲】</note><note n="0189013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，真言【甲】</note><app n="0189013"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">真言</rdg></app>遍數。畢
<lb n="0189a29" ed="T"/><note n="0189014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝竟【甲】</note><note n="0189014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，竟【甲】</note><app n="0189014"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竟</rdg></app>安珠於掌中，頂上合掌迴向發願：「以此
<pb n="0189b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0861.0189b"/>
<lb n="0189b01" ed="T"/>功德，當願眾生速證毘盧遮那佛！」放念珠已，
<lb n="0189b02" ed="T"/>然後結定印，端身正坐於<note n="0189015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頂＋（上）【甲】</note><note n="0189015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂【大】，頂上【甲】</note><app n="0189015"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頂上</rdg></app>中想白色「闇」字；
<lb n="0189b03" ed="T"/>於二目瞳人上想「覽」字，即微屈頭注心於胸
<lb n="0189b04" ed="T"/>臆閒想圓<note n="0189016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝明【甲】</note><note n="0189016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滿【大】，明【甲】</note><app n="0189016"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">明</rdg></app>月輪，於月輪上布列五字；想「阿」
<lb n="0189b05" ed="T"/>字在中央如黃金色，餘四字右旋而安。</p>
<lb n="0189b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189b0601">五字真實義者：</p>
<lb n="0189b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189b0701">「阿」字一切法本不生故；「尾」字思義一切法言
<lb n="0189b08" ed="T"/>說不可得故；「<anchor xml:id="fxT18p0189b01"/>囉」字一切法離塵故；「訶」字一
<lb n="0189b09" ed="T"/>切法因不可得故；「佉」字一<note n="0189017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＋（法）【甲】</note><note n="0189017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切【大】，切法【甲】</note><app n="0189017"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">切法</rdg></app>如虛空<note n="0189018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不可得〕－【甲】</note><note n="0189018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不可得【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0189018"><lem wit="【大】">不可
<lb n="0189b10" ed="T"/>得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>故。名為心念誦。</p>
<lb n="0189b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189b1101">即結劍印，誦七遍頂上散；復結五供養印，獻
<lb n="0189b12" ed="T"/>閼伽讚歎；結不<note n="0189019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">動＋（尊）【甲】</note><note n="0189019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">動【大】，動尊【甲】</note><app n="0189019"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">動尊</rdg></app>劍印，左旋解界；結三<note n="0189020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昧＋（耶）【甲】</note><note n="0189020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">昧【大】，昧耶【甲】</note><app n="0189020"><lem wit="【大】">昧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">昧耶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189b13" ed="T"/>印安於頂上誦三遍，想奉送聖眾。</p><p xml:id="pT18p0189b1314" rend="inline">禮佛而起，
<lb n="0189b14" ed="T"/>隨意經行，讀誦大乘方廣經典，以福迴施一
<lb n="0189b15" ed="T"/>切眾生，願速圓滿心所求，世閒、出世閒悉地
<lb n="0189b16" ed="T"/>成就也。</p>
<lb n="0189b17" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>毘盧遮那念誦<note n="0189021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一卷＝經【甲】</note><note n="0189021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，經【甲】</note><app n="0189021"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb n="0189b18" ed="T"/><note n="0189022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔延享…焉〕五十五字－【甲】</note><note n="0189022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（延享…焉）五十五字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0189022" cb:word-count="55"><lem wit="【大】"><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT18p0189b1801">延享改元，夏，用亡弟僧尊隆遺財而刻是軌，
<lb n="0189b19" ed="T"/>以遂其宿志，伏祈法乳永潤法界云　藤原
<lb n="0189b20" ed="T"/>常香謹誌。</p>
<lb n="0189b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0189b2101">時延享元甲子秋八月，念三豐山無等讐挍
<lb n="0189b22" ed="T"/>焉。</p></cb:div></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
